-venom-more-villains-and-more-drama-040056520.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-spider-man-2-story-trailer-teases-more-venom-more-villains-and-more-drama-040056520.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d93a2783-5cbb-4fa3-ab66-3f6af1a90ee1</guid><dc:creator>肖恩·巴克利</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jul 2023 04:00:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689899582</ingested><modified> 2023-07-21T00:33:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sean Buckley]]></category><media:content height="918" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/c4477a70-275b-11ee-bfad-9aac6841de21" width="1632"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="918" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/c4477a70-275b-11ee-bfad-9aac6841de21" width="1632"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[PlayStation]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Venom appears in the Story Trailer for 'Marvel's Spider-Man 2']]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Spider-Man 2 Story Trailer]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[FTC puts internal trial over Microsoft-Activision deal on hold]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/ftc/">美国联邦贸易委员会</a>已正式搁置对微软收购动视暴雪的行政审判。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-07-20/ftc-to-pause-microsoft-merger-trial-allowing-settlement-talks?sref=10lNAhZ9"><em>彭博社</em></a>最先报道了这一举措，此举使得该机构和公司能够就这项令人瞠目结舌的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-eu-approves-microsofts-687-billion-activision-blizzard-takeover-160319415.html">687 亿美元</a>合并的和解协议进行谈判。</p><p>联邦贸易委员会暂停审理此案的决定是微软和动视暴雪试图完成交易的又一重大胜利。该机构<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ftc-microsoft-activision-blizzard-antitrust-competition-lawsuit-191341476.html">于 12 月提起诉讼，要求阻止该交易</a>，并定于 8 月 2 日举行该案的证据听证会。上周，该公司在一项<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/appeals-court-rejects-the-ftcs-last-ditch-attempt-to-stop-microsoft-from-buying-activision-233137222.html">阻止两家公司合并的</a><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsofts-activision-acquisition-moves-ahead-as-judge-rejects-ftc-injunction-request-152845890.html">法律诉讼中失败</a>，行政审判定于八月初开始。联邦贸易委员会已对其法院败诉提出上诉。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>杰奎琳·斯科特·科利 (Jacqueline Scott Corley) 在上周的裁决中写道：“联邦贸易委员会并没有表明，它的断言可能会成功，合并后的公司可能会从索尼 PlayStation 上撤下《使命召唤》，或者其对动视内容的所有权将大大减少视频游戏库订阅和云游戏市场的竞争。”此后，微软与索尼签署了一项协议，如果合并成功<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-sony-agree-to-keep-call-of-duty-on-playstation-142246583.html">，《使命召唤》将在 PlayStation 上保留 10 年</a>。</p><p>在<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.ftc.gov/system/files/ftc_gov/pdf/608235.respondents_joint_motion_to_withdraw_from_adjudication_v6_publicfor_filing_1.pdf">周二提交的一项动议</a>中，微软和动视敦促联邦贸易委员会撤回其案件。联邦贸易委员会规则规定，该机构必须在两家公司提出请求后撤回案件，因为阻止它们合并的初步禁令被驳回。据<em>彭博社报道</em>，微软和动视现在可以尝试说服联邦贸易委员会接受补救措施，以解决该机构对该交易对游戏行业竞争影响的担忧。或者，他们可以说服联邦贸易委员会完全放弃对合并的反对。</p><p>合并结束后，联邦贸易委员会仍然可以选择举行行政审判。然而，该机构很少在联邦法院败诉后继续处理内部案件。</p><p>收购完成的最初截止日期是周二，不过微软和动视<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-activision-extend-the-deadline-for-their-687-billion-merger-to-october-18th-132138900.html">将合并协议延长</a>至 10 月 18 日，以便给他们“更多的时间来解决剩余的监管问题”。他们一致认为，如果交易失败，微软将承担高达 45 亿美元的分手费，不过双方都决心结束此事。</p><p>微软和动视暴雪仍需获得英国监管机构的批准才能完成交易，而不必采取变通办法继续在该国开展业务。竞争与市场管理局最初<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uk-regulator-blocks-microsofts-activision-blizzard-merger-over-cloud-concerns-113517255.html">于 4 月份阻止了此次合并</a>，但在过去一周左右的时间里，它已<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-uk-regulators-agree-to-pause-legal-fight-to-negotiate-activision-acquisition-165856989.html">表示愿意友好</a>地解决该交易对云游戏市场潜在影响的担忧。</p><p>微软准备向 CMA 提交更新的合并提案。监管机构将于<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uk-competition-regulator-extends-microsoft-activision-investigation-by-six-weeks-103541516.html">8 月 29 日之前做出决定</a>，但其目标是尽快做出决定。 <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-and-a-uk-regulator-have-been-granted-more-time-to-resolve-activision-merger-issues-191354797.html">在本周的听证会上</a>，CMA 的一名律师表示，监管机构和微软都相信该公司能够解决其担忧。这是游戏史上最大的合并很可能在未来几周内完成的又一个迹象。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/ftc-puts-internal-trial-over-microsoft-activision-deal-on-hold-230513417.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/ftc-puts-internal-trial-over-microsoft-activision-deal-on-hold-230513417.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7e90de08-61df-4188-bd8e-714371d8d9e4</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jul 2023 23:05:13 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689894378</ingested><modified> 2023-07-20T23:06:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Mergers, Acquisitions & Takeovers]]></category><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Investment & Company Information]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CD